{"tid":727708,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港股小股災，李小加：毋須大驚小怪","createTime":"2018-07-03T08:34:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T08:59:40.000Z","uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"54e86530b948865ea0c8941d923911abc259cc72","tid":727708,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180703/photo/bkn-20180703123932432-0703_00842_001_01p.jpg?20180703142144\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180703%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180703123932432-0703_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20180703142144&h=b3d82539&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港股今早曾顯著下挫近千點，一度失守28,000點大關，香港交易所(00388)行政總裁李小加在債券通周年論壇後稱，周一(2日)港股因假期休市，而其他市場均有開市，其中A股有較大震盪，加上最近國際形勢不明朗，貿易戰陰霾仍在，影響投資情緒，股市波動屬正常反應，市場毋須大驚小怪，強調香港市場「見過世面」。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他表示，北向債券通已推出一年，推出以來發展順利，期望繼續加強債券通服務，以及不斷改進，令債券通更市場化、更有競爭力。而南向債券通未來定會出現，短期內仍有很多工作要做。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被問及股市大跌是否與人民幣下跌有關，他回應，一般而言，匯率、股市、利率市場均是互相牽動，近期人民幣波動較大，反映人民幣市場制度已經「起來了」，一旦發生問題，人民幣匯率變化亦變得敏感。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180703/mobile/bkn-20180703123932432-0703_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180703%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180703123932432-0703_00842_001.html&d=Hbpg4j%2F5NhQYtgRbQA9tJPM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=c54f7418\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180703/mobile/bkn-20180703123932432-0703_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f7bc7b2f7298beca8b826ddcf9c4cbd614e7b765","tid":727708,"uid":159798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> cow3 is coming to town"},{"pid":"e32ccd00426d7170ac1a73e5eaacddee20f2eac4","tid":727708,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:38:21.000Z","msg":"你屌家"},{"p